@startuml 系统维护模块用例图

left to right direction

actor "系统维护员" as Maintainer
actor "学校管理员" as Admin

usecase "查询系统状态" as UC1
usecase "教室管理" as UC2
usecase "查询教室列表" as UC3
usecase "创建教室" as UC4
usecase "编辑教室" as UC5
usecase "删除教室" as UC6

Maintainer --> UC1
Admin --> UC2
Admin --> UC3
Admin --> UC4
Admin --> UC5
Admin --> UC6

UC2 .> UC3 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC4 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC5 : <<include>>
UC2 .> UC6 : <<include>>

note right of UC1
  检查系统健康状态
  数据库连接状态等
end note

@enduml